# Command Summary

| Command            | Description                    |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------ |
| `/spl`             | Show help menu                 |
| `/spl help`        | Show command help              |
| `/spl info`        | Display protection information |
| `/spl reload`      | Reload configuration           |
| `/spl preview`     | Preview protected area         |
| `/spl setcenter`   | Set custom spawn center        |
| `/spl resetcenter` | Reset custom center            |

